{"word":"H5594 - סָפַד - çâphad - saw-fad' - Lament","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סָפַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>çâphad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>saw-fad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Lament"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துக்கங்கொண்டாடு, துக்கி, புலம்பு, இழவு கொண்டாடு, புலம்பப்படு, மார்பில் அடித்துக்கொள்தல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to wail, to lament, to mourn"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to wail, to lament"},{"paragraph":"2) wailers (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be lamented, to be bewailed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>tear</i> the hair and <i>beat</i> the breasts (as Orientals do in grief); generally to <i>lament</i>; by implication to <i>wail: - </i>lament, mourn (-er), wail."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4553 - מִסְפֵּד - miçpêd - mis-pade'/4553\">H4553</a>, <a href=\"#/H5594 - סָפַד - çâphad - saw-fad'/5594\">H5594</a>"}]}